        Fills out default BML keypositions that are not yet in the TimedMotionUnit. Conventions: missing ready => ready = start = 0; missing relax => relax = end = 1; missing strokeStart => strokeStart = ready missing strokeEnd => strokeEnd = relax missing stroke => stroke = strokeStart
